Transform plain text into a visually stunning Knowledge Graph with GPT-3! It converts text into RDF tuples, and highlights the most frequent connections with a vibrant color-coding system. Download the results as a convenient JSON file for easy integration into your own projects.
A curated index to track AI-powered products.

Essentials is a socially conscious e-commerce platform that aims to reduce food waste and mitigate global warming through the sale of surplus edible foods and fruits. The project won the Regional Finals out of over 850 projects in the Microsoft Imagine Cup 2020 competition, and was nominated for the National Finals.

Pagebook is a cross-platform collaborative document editor designed for team collaboration. It is built using ReactJS and NodeJS, with real-time collaboration features powered by SocketIO. Teams across the world can work together on documents in real-time, ensuring seamless and efficient teamwork. Pagebook is an essential tool for modern-day teams

Thulla Engine is a powerful multiplayer game engine built in Elixir that enables online players to play a popular card game from anywhere in the world. The game logic is handled through the use of Elixir's pattern matching, making the engine both efficient and reliable.

The Passport and ID Card Image Dataset is a collection of over 500 images of passports and ID cards, specifically created for the purpose of training RCNN models for image segmentation using Coco Annotator. The dataset includes high-quality images of passports and ID cards, covering a diverse range of countries, nationalities and designs.
